Tyvärr har jag lite trångt på disken just nu, och en DVD tar ju en del plats.

Fånigt egentligen, att inte ha ordentligt med plats, nu när en 80-giggare kostar runt 500:-. Eftersom jag är för gammal för att tro på tomten, så borde jag egentligen åka och köpa en ny disk på stört... :)

Du borde köpa ny på stört.
Om du gillar Stones måste du ha denna här filmen, det är en klockren inblick i när de var som störst.

Almost three years now, since I started this torrent. 1779 downloads just now, but rarely more than one single seeder (beside me). Depressing, isn't it?

And just one star for the quality? It's the frigging CDs in it's original form, for crying out loud!?!?! How much better can the quality get???

Jeezz guys, you all sure are a sorry bunch of leechers. Did I hear "thank you"" somewhere? Yes, once (fabre), but not 1779 times for sure.

Did I hear "wow, this is great, I'll seed it for months now"? No, I did not. So I wonder why I even bother with this fucking TPB at all... :(
This is AWESOME, thank you Baloo.  I've been looking for this.

Almost three years ago I wondered why I bothered. Now I know.

My package went corrupt in a disk crash, so rather than ripping it all again, I tried my old torrent. And, what did I find? It's still active!

Thanks a million to you guys that has kept this torrent going for all those years. I love y'all!
